  </p>
  <ul class="text-sm font-light pl-5 list-disc grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-4 gap-y-1">
    <li><strong>JavaScript / TypeScript</strong></li>
    <li><strong>Node.js + Express</strong></li>
    <li><strong>PHP (Laravel 8+)</strong></li>
    <li><strong>MySQL</strong></li>
    <li><strong>React + Astro</strong></li>
    <li><strong>AWS S3 & Lambda</strong></li>
  </ul>
</Card>
